<!-- ===================== UNANSWERED ===================== -->
<section id="cat-unanswered" aria-labelledby="cat-unanswered-heading">
  <h2 id="cat-unanswered-heading">Unanswered</h2>
  <p>
    Questions that receive no clear response. Usually caused by ambiguity,
    overload, or diffusion of responsibility.
  </p>

  <!-- 5/5 -->
  <section
    id="orphaned"
    data-term="orphaned"
    aria-labelledby="orphaned-heading"
  >
    <h3 id="orphaned-heading">Orphaned</h3>
    <p>A direct question receives no reply.</p>
    <dl>
      <dt>Next step</dt>
      <dd>
        Reply-all, quote the exact question, suggest owner and soft deadline.
      </dd>
      <dt>Prevention</dt>
      <dd>
        Always name a
        <a
          href="https://handbook.gitlab.com/handbook/people-group/directly-responsible-individuals/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <abbr title="Directly Responsible Individual">DRI</abbr>
        </a>
        when asking.
      </dd>
      <dt>Commonality</dt>
      <dd>
        <meter value="5" min="0" max="5" title="5/5">5 out of 5</meter>
      </dd>
      <dt>Channel</dt>
      <dd>Public. Neutral tone. Quote verbatim.</dd>
      <dt>If next step fails</dt>
      <dd>Escalate to explicit decision request or 1:1 key actor.</dd>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <!-- 5/5 -->
  <section
    id="overlooked"
    data-term="overlooked"
    aria-labelledby="overlooked-heading"
  >
    <h3 id="overlooked-heading">Overlooked</h3>
    <p>Question buried in noise.</p>
    <dl>
      <dt>Next step</dt>
      <dd>Re-ask succinctly. Isolate single question.</dd>
      <dt>Prevention</dt>
      <dd>One clear ask per paragraph.</dd>
      <dt>Commonality</dt>
      <dd>
        <meter value="5" min="0" max="5" title="5/5">5 out of 5</meter>
      </dd>
      <dt>Channel</dt>
      <dd>Public. Minimal prose.</dd>
      <dt>If next step fails</dt>
      <dd>Start new focused thread.</dd>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <!-- 4/5 -->
  <section
    id="dangling"
    data-term="dangling"
    aria-labelledby="dangling-heading"
  >
    <h3 id="dangling-heading">Dangling</h3>
    <p>Conversation pauses mid-resolution.</p>
    <dl>
      <dt>Next step</dt>
      <dd>Summarize state and propose concrete next action.</dd>
      <dt>Prevention</dt>
      <dd>End threads with explicit next step.</dd>
      <dt>Commonality</dt>
      <dd>
        <meter value="4" min="0" max="5" title="4/5">4 out of 5</meter>
      </dd>
      <dt>Channel</dt>
      <dd>Public. Short numbered summary.</dd>
      <dt>If next step fails</dt>
      <dd>Timebox: proceed if no objections.</dd>
    </dl>
  </section>

  <!-- 3/5 -->
  <section id="ghosted" data-term="ghosted" aria-labelledby="ghosted-heading">
    <h3 id="ghosted-heading">Ghosted</h3>
    <p>Individual disengages silently.</p>
    <dl>
      <dt>Next step</dt>
      <dd>1:1 check-in. Ask if blocked.</dd>
      <dt>Prevention</dt>
      <dd>Agree on response norms.</dd>
      <dt>Commonality</dt>
      <dd>
        <meter value="3" min="0" max="5" title="3/5">3 out of 5</meter>
      </dd>
      <dt>Channel</dt>
      <dd>Private first. Assume good intent.</dd>
      <dt>If next step fails</dt>
      <dd>Escalate publicly with neutral framing.</dd>
    </dl>
  </section>
</section>
